languages.text: "Ты несешь эту привилегию с большим достоинством, чем Теодора. В темный час Император послал Простору достойного вожака в твоем лице".
"You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."
languages.original_text: "Ты несешь эту привилегию с большим достоинством, чем Теодора. В темный час Император послал Простору достойного вожака в твоем лице".

languages.text: "Ihr tragt dieses Privileg mit größerer Würde als Theodora es tat. In dieser dunklen Stunde hat der Imperator {mf|einen würdigen Anführer|eine würdige Anführerin} geschickt, um die Ausdehnung zu lenken."
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."

languages.text: « C'est un privilège dont vous disposez avec bien plus d'honneur que Théodora. En ces heures sombres, l'Empereur a envoyé {mf|un berger|une bergère} digne de ce nom pour guider les Étendues. »
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."

languages.text: 「あなたはシオドーラ以上の威厳をもってこの特権を担っている。この暗黒の時代にあって、皇帝はエクスパンスを導くにふさわしい指導者を遣わされたようだ」
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."

traits.locale_text: 「あなたはシオドーラ以上の威厳をもってこの特権を担っている。この暗黒の時代にあって、皇帝はエクスパンスを導くにふさわしい指導者を遣わされたようだ」

languages.text: «Porta este privilegio con mayor dignidad de la que nunca mostró Theodora. En estos tiempos fatídicos, el Emperador ha enviado a un{mf||a} líder excepcional para guiar a la Extensión».
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."

traits.locale_text: «Porta este privilegio con mayor dignidad de la que nunca mostró Theodora. En estos tiempos fatídicos, el Emperador ha enviado a un{mf||a} líder excepcional para guiar a la Extensión».

languages.text: “你比西奥多拉更有资格拥有行商浪人的名号。在这黑暗的时刻，帝皇派来了一位值得尊敬的领袖，指引科罗努斯扩区的未来。”
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."

languages.text: "Bu imtiyazı Theodora'dan daha onurlu bir şekilde taşıyorsun. İmparator, bu karanlık zamanlarda Enginlik'e yol göstermesi için değerli bir lider göndermiş."
languages.original_text: "You bear this privilege with greater dignity than Theodora did. In this dark hour, the Emperor has sent a worthy leader to guide the Expanse."
